s%20stock%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1823138%2F000090266425004376%2Fp25-2168dfan14a.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20lengthy%20presentation%20that%20outlined%20its%20myriad%20objections%20to%20the%20takeover%2C%20including%20that%20it%20was%20not%20profitable%20enough%20for%20stock%20owners.%20The%20firm%20urged%20investors%20to%20reject%20it%20in%20the%20upcoming%20shareholder%20vote%20on%20October%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Livingston%2C%20New%20Jersey-based%20CoreWeave%20said%20the%20acquisition%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20compelling%20path%20forward%20for%20Core%20Scientific%20stockholders%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20present%20deal%20would%20be%20its%20%26quot%3Bbest%20and%20final%26quot%3B%20offer%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20combination%20will%20offer%20Core%20Scientific%20and%20CoreWeave%20stockholders%20the%20opportunity%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20tremendous%20upside%20potential%20and%20long-term%20value%20creation%20driven%20by%20greater%20verticalization%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Intrator%2C%20CoreWeave's%20CEO%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20published%20on%20October%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntrator%20said%20the%20complaints%20from%20Two%20Seas%20Capital%20were%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%20and%20misinformed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoreWeave's%20rapid%2C%20debt-fueled%20growth%20has%20thrust%20it%20into%20the%20center%20of%20a%20growing%20debate%20over%20whether%20AI%20speculation%20has%20become%20a%20bubble%20or%20if%20early%20movers%20like%20it%20are%20seizing%20on%20a%20historic%20investment%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20CoreWeave%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coreweave.com%2Fnews%2Fcoreweave-to-acquire-core-scientific%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20had%20reached%20an%20agreement%20to%20buy%20Core%20Scientific%20in%20a%20stock%20conversion%20deal%20that%20valued%20Core%20Scientific%20at%20roughly%20%249%20billion%20at%20the%20time%20and%20%2420.40%20per%20share%20%E2%80%94%20a%2066%25%20per%20share%20premium%20over%20what%20Core%20Scientific%20stock%20had%20then%20been%20recently%20trading%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20ensuing%20months%2C%20the%20economics%20have%20shifted%20as%20CoreWeave's%20shares%20have%20dipped%20and%20Core%20Scientific's%20have%20risen.%20The%20stock%20conversion%20deal%20currently%20values%20Core%20Scientific's%20shares%20at%20around%20%2417%2C%20more%20than%2010%25%20below%20its%20market%20price%20of%20about%20%2419%20on%20Friday.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ECoreWeave%20and%20Core%20Scientific%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20popular%20deal%2C%20I%20think%20for%20one%20simple%20reason%3A%20it's%20a%20flawed%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20a%20deal%20that%20would%20value%20my%20shares%2C%20actually%2C%20at%20a%20discount%20to%20what%20they%20currently%20trade%20for%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a3c13f8-6d57-4654-ab21-9c8717480f86%5C%22%3EFast%20growth%20and%20mounting%20costs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-ipo-stock-price-crwv-ai-nvidia-tech-stocks-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshaky%20initial%20public%20offering%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%2C%20CoreWeave%20has%20raced%20to%20a%20%2470%20billion%20market%20capitalization%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20three%20times%20its%20value%20after%20the%20IPO%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20place%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20booming%20data%20center%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20announced%20blockbuster%20deals%20with%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-computing-deals-1-trillion-nvda-amd-orcl-crwv-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Meta%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20the%20chipmaker%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20has%20spent%20billions%20of%20dollars%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coreweave.com%2Fnews%2Fcoreweave-to-acquire-openpipe-leader-in-reinforcement-learning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnapping%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20AI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coreweave.com%2Fblog%2Fcoreweave-completes-acquisition-of-weights-biases%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelopers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coreweave.com%2Fnews%2Fcoreweave-to-acquire-monolith-expanding-ai-cloud-platform-into-industrial-innovation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloud%3C%2Fa%3E%20providers%20to%20broaden%20its%20capabilities%20and%20customer%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20company's%20second-quarter%20earnings%20call%2C%20Intrator%20said%20that%20its%20biggest%20customers%20required%20the%20development%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20including%20data%20centers%2C%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bplanetary%26quot%3B%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20aggressively%20expanding%20our%20footprint%20on%20the%20back%20of%20intensifying%20demand%20signals%20from%20our%20customers%2C%20ensuring%20that%20we%20maintain%20a%20durable%2C%20multi-year%20runway%20for%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Intrator%2C%20CoreWeave's%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%2C%20said%20in%20the%20company's%20second%20quarter%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoreWeave%20said%20it%20is%20expanding%20its%20roughly%20470%20megawatts%20of%20operating%20data%20centers%20to%20more%20than%20900%20megawatts%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20power%20to%20light%20up%20about%20a%20fifth%20of%20New%20York%20City%20on%20an%20average%20day.%20The%20Core%20Scientific%20acquisition%20would%20more%20than%20double%20that%20by%20operational%20megawattage%20and%20expand%20the%20company's%20pipeline%20of%20contracted%20future%20power%20by%2050%25%20to%20more%20than%203%20gigawatts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERevenue%20for%20CoreWeave%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20was%20%241.2%20billion%2C%20more%20than%20double%20the%20same%20period%20a%20year%20prior%2C%20the%20company%20reported%2C%20and%20its%20revenue%20backlog%20of%20%2430.1%20billion%20had%20doubled%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year%20%E2%80%94%20demonstrating%20its%20tremendous%20business%20prospects.%20Its%20operating%20margins%2C%20however%2C%20fell%20from%2020%25%20to%202%25%20year%20over%20year%2C%20a%20sign%20of%20how%20costs%20are%20increasingly%20eating%20into%20the%20company's%20profitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20reported%20its%20debt%20had%20grown%20to%20%2411.2%20billion%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20second%20quarter%2C%20a%2040%25%20increase%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year%2C%20and%20that%20its%20borrowing%20costs%20ranged%20from%207%25%20to%2015%25%20on%20its%20various%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGil%20Luria%2C%20an%20analyst%20who%20covers%20the%20company%2C%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20high-cost%20borrowing%20compared%20to%20the%20company's%20slimmer%20profit%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20selling%20%2420%20bills%20for%2015%20bucks%2C%26quot%3B%20Luria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20we%20forget%20to%20ask%20ourselves%20if%20this%20business%20should%20even%20exist%2C%26quot%3B%20Luria%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20the%20answer%20is%20yes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcquiring%20Core%20Scientific%20would%20streamline%20some%20of%20CoreWeave's%20mounting%20overhead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoreWeave%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesswire.com%2Fnews%2Fhome%2F20240625541641%2Fen%2FCore-Scientific-Announces-New-Contract-with-CoreWeave-for-Delivery-of-Approximately-70-MW-of-Additional-Infrastructure-to-Host-High-Performance-Computing-Operations%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erents%20roughly%20270%20megawatts%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20data%20center%20space%20from%20Core%20Scientific%2C%20and%20owning%20the%20company%20would%20allow%20CoreWeave%20to%20save%20about%20%2410%20billion%20in%20lease%20payments%20for%20that%20space%20over%20the%20next%2012%20years%2C%20it%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20realize%20how%20important%20this%20is%20to%20the%20long-term%20viability%20of%20their%20business%20model%2C%20owning%20the%20economics%20around%20their%20largest%20cost%2C%20which%20is%20data%20centers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Raul%20Martynek%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20data%20center%20developer%20and%20operator%20DataBank%2C%20which%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartynek%20said%20that%20Intrator's%20response%20letter%20signified%20the%20CEO%20was%20making%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-throated%20defense%20of%20their%20offer%26quot%3B%20to%20purchase%20Core%20Scientific.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227782fb38-211c-4f21-9d42-4d52d514b34d%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20hot%20data%20center%20market%2C%20is%20Core%20Scientific%20worth%20more%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20concerns%20outlined%20in%20its%20presentation%2C%20Two%20Seas%20said%20that%20the%20deal%20didn't%20offer%20shareholders%20protection%20from%20stock%20fluctuations%20that%20have%20upended%20the%20economics%20of%20the%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20initial%20headline%20deal%20price%20of%20%2420.40%20per%20share%20undervalued%20Core%20Scientific's%20intrinsic%20value%20and%20strategic%20value%20to%20CoreWeave%2C%26quot%3B%20Two%20Seas%20Capital%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BFollowing%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20post-deal%20drawdowns%20in%20an%20acquirer's%20stock%20price%20since%202020%3B%20the%20current%20deal%20value%20of%20less%20than%20%2418%20per%20share%20reflects%20a%20take-under%20of%20Core%20Scientific.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Intrator%20wrote%20that%20CoreWeave%20represents%20Core%20Scientific's%20only%20meaningful%20data%20center%20customer%20and%20that%20its%20business%20accounts%20for%2076%25%20of%20Core%20Scientific's%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntrator%20added%20that%20Core%20Scientific%20investors%20should%20%26quot%3Bthink%20objectively%20about%20Core%20Scientific's%20stand-alone%20prospects%20and%20the%20significant%20risks%20involved%26quot%3B%20in%20rejecting%20the%20deal%20and%20remaining%20an%20independent%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiller%20disagreed%2C%20stating%20that%20in%20a%20hot%20data%20center%20market%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20belief%20is%2C%20if%20you%20leave%20this%20company%20alone%20for%2018%20months%2C%20it's%20a%20%2430%20to%20%2440%20company%26quot%3B%20per%20share%2C%20and%20that%20he%20felt%20it%20could%20be%20a%20more%20lucrative%20acquisition%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcore-scientific-shareholder-oppose-coreweave-takeover-bid-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760737449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f2a1465dbc4fd10dab16d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcore-scientific-shareholder-oppose-coreweave-takeover-bid-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CoreWeave's%20deal%20to%20acquire%20a%20data%20center%20partner%20is%20in%20jeopardy%20after%20shareholders%20oppose%20the%20transaction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dgeiger%40businessinsider.com%20(Daniel%20Geiger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcore-scientific-shareholder-oppose-coreweave-takeover-bid-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jackie%20Shroff%20rebukes%20paps%20at%20Pankaj%20Dheer's%20prayer%20meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760737274000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-124646403%2Cimgsize-40208.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.co