%20Marc%20Benioff%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20apologized%20for%20suggesting%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20should%20call%20the%20National%20Guard%20into%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20listened%20closely%20to%20my%20fellow%20San%20Franciscans%20and%20our%20local%20officials%2C%20and%20after%20the%20largest%20and%20safest%20Dreamforce%20in%20our%20history%2C%20I%20do%20not%20believe%20the%20National%20Guard%20is%20needed%20to%20address%20safety%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%26quot%3B%20Benioff%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20earlier%20comment%20came%20from%20an%20abundance%20of%20caution%20around%20the%20event%2C%20and%20I%20sincerely%20apologize%20for%20the%20concern%20it%20caused%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20my%20firm%20belief%20that%20our%20city%20makes%20the%20most%20progress%20when%20we%20all%20work%20together%20in%20a%20spirit%20of%20partnership.%20I%20remain%20deeply%20grateful%20to%20Mayor%20Lurie%2C%20SFPD%2C%20and%20all%20our%20partners%2C%20and%20am%20fully%20committed%20to%20a%20safer%2C%20stronger%20San%20Francisco.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenioff%20has%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrett-adcock-figureai-humanoid-robot-new-species-dreamforce-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethis%20year's%20Dreamforce%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company's%20annual%20conference%2C%20was%20the%20largest%20in%20its%20history%2C%20with%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-marc-benioff-ai-half-work-layoffs-employees-question-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E50%2C000%20attendees.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20conference%2C%20Benioff%20made%20repeated%20references%20to%20safety%2C%20and%20at%20one%20point%20said%20the%20company%20hired%20hundreds%20of%20its%20own%20security%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20initial%20comments%20urging%20the%20president%20to%20call%20the%20National%20Guard%20into%20the%20city%20were%20made%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20that%20was%20published%20on%20October%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20reached%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Salesforce%20declined%20to%20comment%20further%20than%20Benioff's%20remarks.%20Salesforce%20has%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20whether%20there's%20been%20a%20major%20safety-related%20incident%20at%20a%20Dreamforce%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProminent%20venture%20capitalist%20Ron%20Conway%20resigned%20from%20the%20board%20of%20the%20Salesforce%20Foundation%2C%20the%20software%20company's%20philanthropic%20arm%2C%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%20that%20Conway%20sent%20Benioff%20an%20email%20saying%20their%20%26quot%3Bvalues%20were%20no%20longer%20aligned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20saddens%20me%20immensely%20to%20say%20that%20with%20your%20recent%20comments%2C%20and%20failure%20to%20understand%20their%20impact%2C%20I%20now%20barely%20recognize%20the%20person%20I%20have%20so%20long%20admired%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Times%20reported%20Conway%2C%20a%20top%20Democratic%20donor%2C%20wrote%20to%20Benioff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce%20confirmed%20Conway's%20departure%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20deep%20gratitude%20for%20Ron%20Conway%20and%20his%20incredible%20contributions%20to%20the%20Salesforce%20Foundation%20Board%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComedians%20Kumail%20Nanjiani%20and%20Ilana%20Glazer%20also%20canceled%20performances%20at%20Dreamforce%2C%20but%20did%20not%20specify%20the%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Benioff%20threatened%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-behind-the-scenes-look-at-dreamforce-salesforces-mega-conference-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eto%20move%20Dreamforce%3C%2Fa%3E%20outside%20San%20Francisco%20if%20that%20year's%20event%20was%20affected%20by%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bt