ing%20grounds%2C%20Arctic%20Army%20installations%20and%20ranges%2C%20or%20wet%2C%20hot%20training%20areas%20in%20the%20Pacific.%20Getting%20drones%20to%20perform%20the%20way%20the%20Army%20wants%20has%20been%20a%20challenge%20in%20recent%20years%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20problem%20the%20service%20can't%20ignore%20as%20it%20prepares%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-us-armys-pacific-war-prep-from-unfamiliar-landings-to-drones-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econflict%20with%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Army's%20annual%20gathering%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20this%20week%2C%20Command%20Sgt.%20Maj.%20Shaun%20Curry%20of%20the%2025th%20Infantry%20Division%20said%20that%20some%20drone%20models%20tested%20elsewhere%20struggled%20soon%20after%20arriving%20in%20Hawaii.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20that%20equipment%20came%20to%20Hawaii%2C%20it%20was%20100%20degrees%20outside%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20salt%20water%20in%20the%20air%2C%20Curry%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20drones%20did%20not%20last%20in%20those%20heat%20environments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drones%20were%20sent%20out%20to%20the%2025th%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Army's%20Transformation%20in%20Contact%20initiative%2C%20a%20program%20aiming%20to%20streamline%20the%20process%20of%20soldier-driven%20testing%2C%20integration%2C%20and%20improvement%20of%20new%20weapons.%20Feedback%20from%20that%20work%20is%20implemented%20into%20operational%20planning%20and%20tactics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurry%20said%20that%20when%20the%20drones%20ran%20into%20problems%2C%20the%20developers%20were%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20fix%20them.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20didn't%20work%20right%20then%20and%20there%2C%20they%20would%20work%20on%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%20they%20gave%20you%20a%20new%2C%20upgraded%20version.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArmy%20personnel%20have%20run%20into%20similar%20